IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User pranomestro
PassCmd "spm show pranomestro@gmail"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path "/usr/local/mail/pranomostro/gmail/"
Inbox "/usr/local/mail/pranomostro/gmail/inbox/"
Trash "/usr/local/mail/pranomostro/gmail/trash/"

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "[Gmail].All/Sent Mail" "[Gmail].All/Drafts" "[Gmail].All/Trash" "[Gmail].All/Spam"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount posteo
Host posteo.de
User pranomostro@posteo.net
AuthMechs LOGIN
PassCmd "spm show pranomostro@posteo"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/posteo.crt

IMAPSTore posteo-remote
Account posteo

MaildirStore posteo-local
Path "/usr/local/mail/pranomostro/posteo/"
Inbox "/usr/local/mail/pranomostro/posteo/inbox/"
Trash "/usr/local/mail/pranomostro/posteo/trash/"

Channel posteo
Master :posteo-remote:
Slave :posteo-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Drafts" "Sent" "Trash"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
